    "description": "<strong>Tapeheads</strong> is a retro-futuristic computer simulation game set in an world where technology took a different path. You receive a replica of the 1983 Sonnenlicht Troika computer system from your uncle. Using the Symbolic79 programming language, solve puzzles sent by your uncle and his friends. Take breaks with included mini-games.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Symbolic79 programming language</strong>: Custom language with extensive documentation and examples.<br></li><li><strong>Interpreter with debugging and REPL</strong>: Debug and test your code seamlessly with an interactive interpreter and REPL.<br></li><li><strong>Editor with file revisioning</strong>: Manage your projects with built-in file revisioning.<br></li><li><strong>Mini-games with logic puzzles</strong>: Enjoy engaging mini-games.<br></li><li><strong>Atmospheric sound and graphics</strong>: Immerse yourself in a detailed retro-futuristic system.</li></ul><br><strong>Artwork from the In-Game Magazine</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094680/extras/9aa1a38687ef8367bb0f65ca89746b7b.avif?t=1758553892\" width=600 height=776 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094680/extras/57c0e1a65ee1b453960726c819a7b081.avif?t=1758553892\" width=600 height=776 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094680/extras/bfb862e4e12b7a1d41547b505ad72043.avif?t=1758553892\" width=600 height=776 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094680/extras/5aab9224be90a3cb6567802a7389b6c0.avif?t=1758553892\" width=600 height=776 /></span>",
